<refsect2 id="g-binding-unbind" role="function" condition="since:2.38">
<title>g_binding_unbind&#160;()</title>
<indexterm zone="g-binding-unbind" role="2.38"><primary sortas="binding_unbind">g_binding_unbind</primary></indexterm>
<programlisting language="C"><link linkend="void"><returnvalue>void</returnvalue></link>
g_binding_unbind (<parameter><link linkend="GBinding"><type>GBinding</type></link> *binding</parameter>);</programlisting>
<para>Explicitly releases the binding between the source and the target
property expressed by <parameter>binding</parameter>
.</para>
<para>This function will release the reference that is being held on
the <parameter>binding</parameter>
 instance; if you want to hold on to the <link linkend="GBinding"><type>GBinding</type></link> instance
after calling <link linkend="g-binding-unbind"><function>g_binding_unbind()</function></link>, you will need to hold a reference
to it.</para>
