<row role="constant"><entry role="enum_member_name"><para id="G-BINDING-DEFAULT:CAPS">G_BINDING_DEFAULT</para></entry>
<entry role="enum_member_description"><para>The default binding; if the source property
  changes, the target property is updated with its value.</para>
</entry>
<entry role="enum_member_annotations"></entry>
</row>
<row role="constant"><entry role="enum_member_name"><para id="G-BINDING-BIDIRECTIONAL:CAPS">G_BINDING_BIDIRECTIONAL</para></entry>
<entry role="enum_member_description"><para>Bidirectional binding; if either the
  property of the source or the property of the target changes,
  the other is updated.</para>
</entry>
<entry role="enum_member_annotations"></entry>
</row>
<row role="constant"><entry role="enum_member_name"><para id="G-BINDING-SYNC-CREATE:CAPS">G_BINDING_SYNC_CREATE</para></entry>
